CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F433A1780323077
OL,3,CWorld's largest crane lifts plant's
OL,4,Csecond nuclear reactor into place
OL,6,FThe world's largest crane, known as
OL,7,F"Big Carl", has lifted Hinkley Point
OL,8,FC's second nuclear reactor into place.
OL,10,FThe nuclear power plant in Somerset is
OL,11,Fowned by EDF Energy, which says the
OL,12,Ftwo reactors will power six million
OL,13,Fhomes, cutting the country's reliance
OL,14,Fon imported fossil fuels.
OL,16,FHinkley's first reactor was lifted
OL,17,Fusing a large temporary overhead
OL,18,Flifting system, but EDF says using Big
OL,19,FCarl saved it space, time and money.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G1/5
