FL,434,430,120,260,000,100
PN,43302
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F433A1780323077
OL,3,CWorld's largest crane lifts plant's
OL,4,Csecond nuclear reactor into place
OL,6,FEDF said: "Once inside the reactor
OL,7,Fbuilding, the 13-metre-long reactor
OL,8,Fpressure vessel was lifted and rotated
OL,9,Finto a vertical position by the large
OL,10,Finternal "polar" crane and lowered
OL,11,Fcarefully onto a support ring with
OL,12,Fjust 40mm clearance on either side.
OL,14,F"Unit 2 is being built 20-30% more
OL,15,Fquickly than Unit 1, thanks to
OL,16,Finnovation and experience of building
OL,17,Fan identical design with the same
OL,18,Fteams.
OL,26,@rD@JOUrD@PO]
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G2/5
