OL,24,ANext Page BSW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,434,430,120,260,000,100
PN,43303
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F433A1780323077
OL,3,CWorld's largest crane lifts plant's
OL,4,Csecond nuclear reactor into place
OL,6,FThe reactor pressure vessel uses
OL,7,Fnuclear fission to make heat and steam
OL,8,Ffor the world's largest turbines, the
OL,9,FArabelle.
OL,11,FSimon Parsons, Hinkley Point C's
OL,12,FDelivery Director, added: "This marks
OL,13,Fa tremendous achievement by the entire
OL,14,Fteam and one that has taken months of
OL,15,Fplanning and close coordination
OL,16,Fbetween the 10 main contractors
OL,17,Finvolved.
OL,26,@tD@[OU
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G3/5
OL,2,W,.!+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BSW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,434,430,120,260,000,100
PN,43304
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F433A1780323077
OL,3,CWorld's largest crane lifts plant's
OL,4,Csecond nuclear reactor into place
OL,6,F"We've also seen strong innovation to
OL,7,Fachieve not just a 'cut and paste'
OL,8,Ffrom the first reactor's installation,
OL,9,Fbut using our experience to save time,
OL,10,Fmoney and disruption to the site.
OL,12,F"Importantly, we are also applying
OL,13,Fthose lessons to put Unit 2 well ahead
OL,14,Fof the first unit's position at the
OL,15,Fequivalent stage, with more materials
OL,16,Fin place and more work achieved."
OL,26,@tD@AOU
